Outline: This workout app allows users to both register and login to their account and post their workouts for every user to see. Once they have completed their workout, they can post what they have done so that other users can see and use their workout. It makes you describe your workout, how many sets you have done, how many reps, and the duration of the workout. Once you have filled out all the information you can post it so that other users can see and use your workout in the gym to help them. This is done because a lot of the time in the gym, I struggle to find new workouts to do so using this, I can use other peopleâ€™s workouts.

